-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Reference Policy</span><br/></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Supported Profiles</span><p><a href=\"http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-core/7.0.0-ballot/StructureDefinition-ch-core-practitionerrole-epr.html\">CH Core PractitionerRole EPR</a></p></div><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Interaction summary</span><br/><ul><li>Supports <code>update</code>, <code>search-type</code>, <code>read</code>, <code>create</code>.</li></ul></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-7\"><span class=\"lead\">Search Parameters</span><table class=\"table table-condensed table-hover\"><thead><tr><th>Conformance</th><th>Parameter</th><th>Type</th><th>Documentation</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td>code</td><td><code>string</code></td><td><div/></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"col-lg-5\"> </div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 id=\"RelatedPerson1-13\" class=\"panel-title\"><span style=\"float: right;\">Resource Conformance: unspecified </span>RelatedPerson</h4></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Base System Profile</span><br/><a href=\"http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-core/7.0.0-ballot/StructureDefinition-ch-core-relatedperson.html\">CH Core RelatedPerson</a></div><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Profile Conformance</span><br/><b>SHALL</b></div><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Reference Policy</span><br/></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Interaction summary</span><br/><ul><li>Supports <code>update</code>, <code>search-type</code>, <code>read</code>, <code>create</code>.</li></ul></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-7\"><span class=\"lead\">Search Parameters</span><table class=\"table table-condensed table-hover\"><thead><tr><th>Conformance</th><th>Parameter</th><th>Type</th><th>Documentation</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td>code</td><td><code>string</code></td><td><div/></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td>name</td><td><code>string</code></td><td><div><p>A server defined search that may match any of the string fields in the HumanName, including family, give, prefix, suffix, suffix, and/or text</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td>patient</td><td><code>reference</code></td><td><div><p>The patient this related person is related to</p>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"col-lg-5\"> </div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 id=\"Binary1-14\" class=\"panel-title\"><span style=\"float: right;\">Resource Conformance: unspecified </span>Binary</h4></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"lead\">Core FHIR Resource</span><br/><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/binary.html\">Binary</a></div><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"lead\">Reference Policy</span><br/></div><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"lead\">Interaction summary</span><br/><ul><li>Supports <code>update</code>, <code>search-type</code>, <code>read</code>, <code>create</code>.</li></ul></div></div><p/><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-7\"><span class=\"lead\">Search Parameters</span><table class=\"table table-condensed table-hover\"><thead><tr><th>Conformance</th><th>Parameter</th><th>Type</th><th>Documentation</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td>code</td><td><code>string</code></td><td><div/></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"col-lg-5\"> </div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 id=\"Device1-15\" class=\"panel-title\"><span style=\"float: right;\">Resource Conformance: unspecified </span>Device</h4></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"lead\">Core FHIR Resource</span><br/><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/device.html\">Device</a></div><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"lead\">Reference Policy</span><br/></div><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"lead\">Interaction summary</span><br/><ul><li>Supports <code>update</code>, <code>search-type</code>, <code>read</code>, <code>create</code>.</li></ul></div></div><p/><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-7\"><span class=\"lead\">Search Parameters</span><table class=\"table table-condensed table-hover\"><thead><tr><th>Conformance</th><th>Parameter</th><th>Type</th><th>Documentation</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td>code</td><td><code>string</code></td><td><div/></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"col-lg-5\"> </div></div></div></div></div></div>"^^rdf:XMLLiteral ]
  ] ; # 
  fhir:url [
     fhir:v "http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-vacd/CapabilityStatement/ch-vacd-api-capstmt-srv"^^xsd:anyURI ;
     fhir:l <http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-vacd/CapabilityStatement/ch-vacd-api-capstmt-srv>
  ] ; # 
  fhir:version [ fhir:v "7.0.0-ballot"] ; # 
  fhir:name [ fhir:v "CHVACDApiCapabilityStatementServer"] ; # 
  fhir:title [ fhir:v "CH VACD FHIR API CapabilityStatement for server"] ; # 
  fhir:status [ fhir:v "draft"] ; # 
  fhir:date [ fhir:v "2026-03-23T09:43:45.742+01:00"^^xsd:dateTime] ; # 
  fhir:publisher [ fhir:v "HL7 Switzerland"] ; # 
  fhir:contact ( [
     fhir:name [ fhir:v "HL7 Switzerland" ] ;
     fhir:telecom ( [
       fhir:system [ fhir:v "url" ] ;
       fhir:value [ fhir:v "https://www.hl7.ch/" ]
     ] )
  ] ) ; # 
  fhir:description [ fhir:v "CapabilityStatement for CH VACD API (server)."] ; # 
  fhir:jurisdiction ( [
     fhir:coding ( [
       fhir:system [
         fhir:v "urn:iso:std:iso:3166"^^xsd:anyURI ;
         fhir:l <urn:iso:std:iso:3166>
       ] ;
       fhir:code [ fhir:v "CHE" ]
     ] )
  ] ) ; # 
  fhir:copyright [ fhir:v "CC0-1.0"] ; # 
  fhir:kind [ fhir:v "requirements"] ; # 
  fhir:fhirVersion [ fhir:v "4.0.1"] ; # 
  fhir:format ( [ fhir:v "application/fhir+xml"] [ fhir:v "application/fhir+json"] ) ; # 
  fhir:rest ( [
     fhir:mode [ fhir:v "server" ] ;
     fhir:documentation [ fhir:v "The server will handle all resources and also complete vaccination documents" ] ;
     fhir:resource ( [
       fhir:type [ fhir:v "AllergyIntolerance" ] ;
       fhir:profile [
         fhir:v "http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-vacd/StructureDefinition/ch-vacd-allergyintolerances"^^xsd:anyURI ;
         fhir:l <http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-vacd/StructureDefinition/ch-vacd-allergyintolerances>
       ] ;
       fhir:interaction ( [
         fhir:code [ fhir:v "update" ]
       ] [
         fhir:code [ fhir:v "search-type" ]
       ] [
         fhir:code [ fhir:v "read" ]
       ] [
         fhir:code [ fhir:v "create" ]
       ] ) ;
       fhir:searchInclude ( [ fhir:v "*" ] ) ;
       fhir:searchParam ( [
         fhir:name [ fhir:v "code" ] ;
         fhir:type [ fhir:v "token" ] ;
         fhir:documentation [ fhir:v "Code that identifies the allergy or intolerance" ]
       ] [
         fhir:name [ fhir:v "patient" ] ;
         fhir:type [ fhir:v "reference" ] ;
         fhir:documentation [ fhir:v "Who the sensitivity is for" ]
       ] [
         fhir:name [ fhir:v "identifier" ] ;
         fhir:type [ fhir:v "token" ] ;
         fhir:documentation [ fhir:v "Any identifier for the AllergyIntolerance." ]
       ] )
     ] [
       fhir:type [ fhir:v "Condition" ] ;
       fhir:profile [
         fhir:v "http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-vacd/StructureDefinition/ch-vacd-condition"^^xsd:anyURI ;
         fhir:l <http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-vacd/StructureDefinition/ch-vacd-condition>
       ] ;
       fhir:supportedProfile ( [
         fhir:v "http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-vacd/StructureDefinition/ch-vacd-basic-immunization"^^xsd:anyURI ;
         fhir:l <http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-vacd/StructureDefinition/ch-vacd-basic-immunization>
       ] [
         fhir:v "http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-vacd/StructureDefinition/ch-vacd-medical-problems"^^xsd:anyURI ;
         fhir:l <http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-vacd/StructureDefinition/ch-vacd-medical-problems>
       ] [
         fhir:v "http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-vacd/StructureDefinition/ch-vacd-pastillnesses"^^xsd:anyURI ;
         fhir:l <http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-vacd/StructureDefinition/ch-vacd-pastillnesses>
       ] ) ;
       fhir:interaction ( [
         fhir:code [ fhir:v "update" ]
       ] [
         fhir:code [ fhir:v "search-type" ]
       ] [
         fhir:code [ fhir:v "read" ]
       ] [
         fhir:code [ fhir:v "create" ]
       ] ) ;
       fhir:searchInclude ( [ fhir:v "*" ] ) ;
       fhir:searchParam ( [
         fhir:name [ fhir:v "code" ] ;
         fhir:type [ fhir:v "token" ] ;
         fhir:documentation [ fhir:v "Code for the condition" ]
       ] [
         fhir:name [ fhir:v "patient" ] ;
         fhir:type [ fhir:v "reference" ] ;
         fhir:documentation [ fhir:v "Who has the condition?" ]
       ] [
         fhir:name [ fhir:v "identifier" ] ;
         fhir:type [ fhir:v "token" ] ;
         fhir:documentation [ fhir:v "Any identifier for the Condition." ]
       ] )
     ] [
       fhir:type [ fhir:v "Immunization" ] ;
